&lt;/ul&gt;
</summary></entry><entry><title>琉球(沖縄)民謡 - ヒヤミカチ節</title><link href="http://suhen.org/2013-05-11_hiyamakachi_bushi.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2013-05-11T07:15:00+08:00</updated><author><name>suhen</name></author><id>tag:suhen.org,2013-05-11:2013-05-11_hiyamakachi_bushi.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;這首歌聽起來輕快熱情，一下就吸引我的注意。有空再來研究一下沖繩民謠。&lt;/p&gt;
